OL,6,FA teenage girl was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder at the
OL,8,Fschool, also known as Amman Valley
OL,9,FSchool, in Carmarthenshire after two
OL,10,Fteachers and a pupil sustained stab
OL,11,Fwounds on Wednesday morning.
OL,13,FThe teachers, named as Fiona Elias,
OL,14,Fthe head of Year 7, and reportedly
OL,15,Fspecial needs teacher, Liz Hopkin,
OL,16,Fhave since been discharged from
OL,17,Fhospital along with the the pupil. The
OL,18,Farrested girl remains in custody.
